The Windows menu allows switching and rearranging of [[Main_View_Area|Main View Area]] windows.

<span id="Tools"></span>
==Ferramentas==

The following tools are available in this menu:

* [[File:Std_ActivateNextWindow.svg|32px]] [[Std_ActivateNextWindow|Next]]: Activates the next window.

* [[File:Std_ActivatePrevWindow.svg|32px]] [[Std_ActivatePrevWindow|Previous]]: Activates the previous window.

* [[File:Std_TileWindows.svg|32px]] [[Std_TileWindows|Tile]]: Tiles the windows.

* [[File:Std_CascadeWindows.svg|32px]] [[Std_CascadeWindows|Cascade]]: Cascades the windows.

* … The first 10 windows are listed here. Select a window to activate it.

* [[File:Std Windows.svg|32px]] [[Std_Windows|Choose Open Window]]: Opens a dialog box from which a window can be activated. 


